{"tid":1954421,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"而家疫情下去睇牙醫會唔會好危","createTime":"2020-04-01T20:19:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-03T07:40:03.000Z","uid":172495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3f87577f6c127417c91677a3f20414cc1e2e1e33","tid":1954421,"uid":172495,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:19:52.000Z","msg":"一年前剝左隻智慧齒，前面隻牙蛀左<br />\n拖左好耐都無去整，因為無乜痛(我都知衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)<br />\n我知一定要杜牙根<br />\n最近有輕微感覺，<br />\n臨瞓前又好似咬到疑似牙碎<br />\n但係疫情下又覺得張開口比人整驚驚地<br />\n究竟我整唔整好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f7174dca00f762a22be32ab668a50526c7b494c","tid":1954421,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:20:51.000Z","msg":"聽人講會叫人用稀釋漂白水浪口<br />\n我心諗啲牙同啲牙肉仲駛要既"},{"pid":"cb3d38623792af3fdff7054649613f828359baa9","tid":1954421,"uid":20867,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:40:56.000Z","msg":"該死唔駛病<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c7acb48b2db3716964edd61a593e7a9800e56ef","tid":1954421,"uid":3893,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"8f7174dca00f762a22be32ab668a50526c7b494c","tid":1954421,"uid":34047,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:20:51.000Z","msg":"聽人講會叫人用稀釋漂白水浪口<br />\n我心諗啲牙同啲牙肉仲駛要既"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-01T20:55:26.000Z","msg":"前兩星期睇完 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我諗診所仲驚過你<br />\n因為入面口水一定周圍飛 真係好高危其實 <br />\n所以見佢地都係全副武裝 <br />\nbtw  係滿佈福健幫嘅北角有間好黃嘅牙醫診所  <br />\n如果近可以考慮吓幫襯 <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"751486f2e017f08b7a219ef2a4f4e1c1541ec13a","tid":1954421,"uid":103248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3c7acb48b2db3716964edd61a593e7a9800e56ef","tid":1954421,"u